      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a crisp ZF 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement, and the VANOS system has been recently serviced to ensure precise cam timing. With its variable M differential and refreshed suspension bushings, this unit offers the tactile feedback and linear power delivery enthusiasts demand. It is a well-maintained example that balances raw performance with structural integrity.",
