    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i is a stunning example of precision engineering, finished in a sophisticated Deep Sea Blue Metallic that maintains a deep, lustrous shine. As a detail-oriented seller, I have ensured this vehicle has been maintained to a high standard, with a full service history available for review. The interior is draped in premium Canberra Beige Dakota leather; it has been kept strictly smoke-free and vacuumed weekly, showing only very light, natural softening on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is robust\u2014the turbocharged inline-six delivers smooth, effortless power, and the 8-speed transmission shifts imperceptibly. Recent maintenance includes a fresh synthetic oil change and a brake fluid flush. All electronics, including the iDrive navigation and the premium Harman Kardon surround sound system, function perfectly. While you may find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway use, the body is free of major dents or scratches. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you are ready for the road the moment you take the keys. This is a reliable, luxurious, and thoroughly documented sedan for the discerning buyer.",
